{"tid":2008366,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：以往太過依賴美國的科技  疫情反思要自強 貢獻大灣區","createTime":"2020-05-09T03:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T04:06:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a712e8da5fa7eaccc91a1b54073a2a2a9bb595a3","tid":2008366,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:53:46.000Z","msg":"薛永恒：研發項目最重要有利益申報機制避免誤解<br />\n09.05.2020 11:18<br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局長薛永恒出席本台節目時表示，政府可重用口罩的研發費用，是實報實銷，預料8月可以公布相關帳目。他又指，一早已經網羅了香港紡織及成衣研發中心參與項目，而紡織業界的翹楚，或多或少一早與政府及研發中心有關係，強調最重要是有行之有效的利益申報機制，有需要時相關人士要申報及避席會議，避免引起誤解。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">薛永恒又說，本港以往太依賴<del>個別地區</del><span style=\"color: gold;\">美國</span>的科技供應或市場，疫情正好令本港有反思機會、轉危為機，但強調一定要有平和的環境，才可重振經濟。他希望<del>本港</del><span style=\"color: gold;\">大灣區</span>不要受疫情或政治問題困擾，要看到希望和自強。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286244&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1286244%26csid%3D261_341&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d9WqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=18773bea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286244&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"997f1437377b313a51eb4225804147ac13b67841","tid":2008366,"uid":192754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:55:24.000Z","msg":"死撚開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21bfa0b28c73517e0a2df306e8f9956e3c098226","tid":2008366,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:55:27.000Z","msg":"他應該講緊依賴中國🤔 好多零件都要靠中國生產"},{"pid":"fb47eb5501b38be4f1a79dfba88743fd2645fbf1","tid":2008366,"uid":7043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:06:31.000Z","msg":"學識整奶粉先搞其他科技啦支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"